    <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1"> 
     <h2>We’re all about community</h2> 
     <p>Tagboard creates tools to help create and grow online communities. Our goal is to remove as many barriers as possible in order for people with common interests to find each other and interact. Part of our strategy involves equipping brands, organizations, and community managers with cutting-edge technology so they can better cultivate and facilitate their communities, faster, and with less effort.</p> 
    </div> 
