    </div> 
    <div class="col-sm-8"> 
     <h3>Tagboard at a glance</h3> 
     <p>Tagboard was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Redmond, Washington, USA. The Tagboard team is 50/50 product development and business development personnel.</p> 
